Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.53,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的推理龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:12.19,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}推理？ 感觉跟平时风格不太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.24,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}这个特典也进行到第六集了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.11,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}要防止千篇一律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.45,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}所以说不要说这种高次发言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:19.89,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}这样也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.65,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.19,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不 只是在想你会不会又要脱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.26,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不要啦 同样的梗玩两次就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真是这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.09,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那这也来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:33.73,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:36.91,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的两小时悬疑龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:43.28,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}露科亚大人 你就是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:44.78,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真是荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.56,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}说我就是犯人 有什么证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:50.04,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}确实有这样的场景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}杀人现场的监控器已经把你拍下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:55.36,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}已经把你裸奔逃走的画面拍下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:57.06,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}完 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:58.01,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}才刚说完那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.37,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}这不是马上就脱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:02.31,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的封闭空间龙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.72,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}您 您难道就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:10.76,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}解决了好几起无头案件的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.11,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}名侦探 小林托尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:15.06,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是的 比起这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:18.40,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}在还没有发现那个连续无差别杀人犯之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.34,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}今天还是大家一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:21.54,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.14,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}毕竟不知道犯人藏在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.67,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}行动必须要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.57,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}喂 犯人找到了 就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.65,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的密室手法龙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.59,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}犯人用钝器之类的东西杀害了露科亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:37.22,maidragon-screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H3324A7&\frz40.88\pos(392,701.999)}好想脱衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:37.53,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不过 这个房间是密室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:38.87,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}密室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.87,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真的是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.94,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}像这样使用魔法阵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.03,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}其实很简单就可以自由出入了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.99,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}只有你可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.84,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的时刻表诡计龙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}托尔大人 果然在这车上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.86,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}根本没有作案时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.67,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}等一下 难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.87,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}这样的话 就可以充分赶上犯罪的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.19,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}所以说只有你可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.89,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的恐吓信龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.28,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}没想到翔太居然会被绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.61,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}托尔大人 犯人寄来的恐吓信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:16.61,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:17.68,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.69,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不管你在哪里 我都在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.28,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}我会夺走你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.63,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}总有一天 你的心会变成属于我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:25.90,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你最好觉悟吧 小林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.30,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}这是我昨天写的情书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.80,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}因为没有贴邮票所以被退回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.86,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那张情书 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.40,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的福尔摩斯龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.01,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是委托人吧 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:41.75,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:43.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}虽然这么说很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:45.86,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}但是你是正在洗澡中途急忙赶过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.62,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你是怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.16,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那还没完全干透的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:51.96,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}流着汗的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.76,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}而且比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.17,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}这具什么都没穿的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.68,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}已经如实反映了事实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.05,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是是 全裸全裸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.22,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你随意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:02.32,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.31,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}我早就知道 肯定会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:08.75,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那么下一集是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.38,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}终于到了最后一集了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.02,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.30,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}终于要结束了啊
